history.content: Please see @1676. This is an issue with the new system. Unfortunately, it's not likely this will be fixed for Fall '16. You may want to drop yourself and add again because you will not be enrolled unless you have a seat in lecture + lab + discussion. Please note you will end up at the end of the waitlist.
